title.rendered: Lavish 4BHK Apartment For Sale In Westend

content.rendered:
You’re bound to fall in love❤ with this exceptionally built apartment with a modern facade in the most prestigious locations of South Delhi. This Lavish apartment is spread over a sprawling 500yds and has a beautiful green park at the rear.

Westend has a small club with a brand new swimming pool, gym, party lawn, and gated community offering a secured neighborhood.

🏠Available Floors: 1st & 2nd
♕500yds
♕4BHK
♕Westend
♕Italian Modular Kitchen
♕Rear Park
♕Ready To Move In
♕Posh Locality

Lalit Kaushik

Call On 98183-12077 For Site Visit

http://wa.me/919818312077

Follow @royalerealtorsindia on social media
Checkout Our Other Listings Here
ROYALE REALTORS INDIA

Royale Realtors India – Luxury Real Estate

19 DDA Market, Shanti Niketan, New Delhi, Delhi 110021
